It was a gory sight at Chapel of Redemption Agba Dam Housing Estate,  Ilorin,  yesterday, as  a police sergeant attached to  Kwara State Police Command, killed himself after shooting  to death an unidentified lady with same gun in Ilorin.
   
The officer, identified as Olalere Michael with official number F/NO 497093, reportedly killed the lady at about 8:05a.m.
     
The State Police Commissioner, Paul Odama, after a preliminary investigation, said the victims were lovers, whose affairs went sour leading to the dastardly development. 